\f1\i0 \cb1 \strokec2  to the changes in their lives at this point, they\'92re not yet taking an active role. Everything that has happened has pulled the carpet from under their feet and they\'92re still struggling to regain balance. Here\'92s also where you need to \cb5 plant the seeds of their personal transformation\cb1  and everything else major that happens later on.
